Some lessons learnt:

 - When going through border control, check the website first - they normally ask you to go through as a commercial vehicle if you are bringing household goods
 - Have a list of those things with you. This is what the people stamp.
 - First go to the German people. They will stamp your paper.
 - Next go to the swiss people. They will ask you lots of things, look at your vehicle documents and ask to see the car
 - Buy a motorway sticker, and you're good to go!
 
 
